0x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_drake_theweeknd_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_drake_theweeknd_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_drake_theweeknd_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>由人工智能生成的、模仿<a href="/artists/drake">Drake</a>和<a href="/artists/the-weeknd">The Weeknd 的</a>人声合作项目已提交格莱美颁奖典礼审议。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/ai-music-oasis-liam-gallagher-drake-weeknd-3432529">在人工智能绿洲时代，平凡是没有意义的</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首由匿名制作人 Ghostwriter 创作和制作的歌曲《Heart On My Sleeve》在今年早些时候首次出现时，仅在 TikTok 上就在几个小时内爆红，点击量就达到了 1300 万次。</p><p>在 Apple Music、Spotify 和 Tidal 等流行的 DSP 上，这首歌也有数十万次播放—— <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/universal-music-strip-viral-ai-generated-drake-and-the-weeknd-collaboration-from-streaming-platforms-3432055">在环球音乐集团禁止这首歌之前，</a> YouTube 上的观看次数超过 100,000 次。</p><p>现在，Ghostwriter 的一位代表已向<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/09/05/arts/music/ghostwriter-whiplash-travis-scott-21-savage.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow"><em>《纽约时报》</em></a>证实，该歌曲已提交格莱美两个类别的考虑：最佳说唱歌曲和年度歌曲 - 两者均授予歌曲作者，而不是表演者。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="und" dir="ltr">嗨，我是代笔作家。 <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/drake?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#drake</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/aivoice?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#aivoice</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/theweeknd?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#theweeknd</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/ai?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#ai</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/aidrake?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#aidrake</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/theweekndai?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#theweekndai</a> <a href="https://t.co/lUUAHC1Xw8">pic.twitter.com